{"tid":316914,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[DSE未如理想？]加入警隊，實踐抱負！","createTime":"2017-07-11T05:43:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T03:41:56.000Z","uid":19334,"like":4,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"908b08a88b84fe46b2aaafd2f85e370f350ecc7f","tid":316914,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:43:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/01_about_us/vm.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2F01_about_us%2Fvm.html&d=RWfcpYAj8BCAA7VXPsDiDP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=12ffa23f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/01_about_us/vm.html</a> <br />\n<br />\nPC 遴選程序 <br />\n<br />\n1. 初步審核 Initial Screening (IS) <br />\n2. 體能測試 Physical Test (PT) <br />\n3. 小組面試 Group Interview (GI) (唔係叫First In) <br />\n4. 最後面試 Final Interview Board (FIB)(唔係叫Second In) <br />\n5. 品格審查 Vetting <br />\n6. 體格檢驗 Medical Examination (ME)(唔係叫BC) <br />\n7. 警隊覆核委員會 Force Review Board (FRB) <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://1.IS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.IS&d=RWfcpYAj8BCAA7VXPsDiDP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=d18b9f27\" target=\"_blank\">http://1.IS</a>:核對學歷, 度高, 磅重, 測視力 <br />\n<br />\n度高/磅重:男:最 少 1.63 米 及 體 重 50 公 斤 <br />\n女:最 少 1.52 米 及 體 重 42 公 斤 <br />\n<br />\n可 配 戴 眼 鏡 ， 但 必 須 通 過 視 力 測 試 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://2.PT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F2.PT&d=RWfcpYAj8BCAA7VXPsDiDP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=21072b69\" target=\"_blank\">http://2.PT</a>:立地向上跳, 引體上升,一百米來回跑(10x10) <br />\n[計分方法請參考本版最底的體能續分表] <br />\n[300分滿分150分合格] <br />\n<br />\n立地向上跳:男 性 :53.3 厘 米 <br />\n女 性 :38.1 厘 米 <br />\n<br />\n引體上升:男 性 : 7 <br />\n女 性 : 9(腳爭貼地) <br />\n<br />\n一百米(10x10):男 性 :24.8 秒 <br />\n女 性 :28.1 秒 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"http://3.GI:4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.GI%3A4&d=RWfcpYAj8BCAA7VXPsDiDP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=5c9c12d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://3.GI:4</a>-12[/url]個應徵者的小組討論[開波每人1-2分鍾自我介紹] <br />\n<br />\n收Pol.850返屋企填 <br />\n<br />\n4.FIB:自我介紹再問問題等[178必背,5大處,學堂15單元] <br />\n<br />\n5.Vetting:四大範疇[家庭及個人,在學,在職,財務狀&amp;#20917;] <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://6.ME\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F6.ME&d=RWfcpYAj8BCAA7VXPsDiDP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=674632d7\" target=\"_blank\">http://6.ME</a>:驗身[色弱,色差,弱聽,]要小心,吸煙者最好ME前兩個月戒定 <br />\n<br />\n7.FRB:每個人以上所有關都會有個分send去評[汱弱留強,等得越耐越危險] <br />\n<br />\n急救/拯溺/車牌有分加"},{"pid":"be713586398eee7f7a95b40696739209e335c021","tid":316914,"uid":77880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:47:57.000Z","msg":"thx"},{"pid":"891592b84277b3cf8b3b99626a8fef8589ff673d","tid":316914,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T06:25:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cdbff0782ddd939c6dc76a57d0cca661c873995","tid":316914,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T06:28:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>thx</blockquote><br />\nNo thz"},{"pid":"cc0d42fc343368baa91ae2266a69912f35a6ed38","tid":316914,"uid":23902,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T06:57:56.000Z","msg":"做一個愛國家 愛香港的好警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ee9387af1df2e3b61f74a4a4461bb45bb6e61c","tid":316914,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T06:58:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做一個愛國家 愛香港的好警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a978d591b6a435a2d0b84189b412e03822fbac21","tid":316914,"uid":13097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T08:25:36.000Z","msg":"豬sir