7-11T11:29:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/15_recruit/fitness.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2F15_recruit%2Ffitness.html&d=RWfcpYAj8BCAA7VXPsDiDP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=9af82acf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/15_recruit/fitness.html</a><br />\n由2015年10月起，一套新修訂的入職體能測試已進入試行階段。 該套體能測試包括800米跑、4 x 10米穿梭跑、立定跳高和手握肌力測試。新修訂的體能測試項目是根據警務人員日常工作需要相符的體能要求而釐定，而體能要求仍然維持在高水平。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"054ee4715ca07f6f49a3b97cc1b0338b71c59757","tid":316914,"uid":8382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:31:39.000Z","msg":"屋企隻狗想考警犬，有冇咩渠道？"},{"pid":"adcac8520ed8cca427ca26e8dee401a9f8da3abb","tid":316914,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:10:16.000Z","msg":"汪汪汪"},{"pid":"21a3a08c8f39d2b8b8f55c4d1cf29739a9a7e24e","tid":316914,"uid":22479,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:14:13.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家<br />\n暗角打擭 光明磊落？<br />\n屌你老母啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84c5d259faae80b1524a634101e025bf9c862bd4","tid":316914,"uid":19334,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:22:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黑警死全家<br />\n暗角打擭 光明磊落？<br />\n屌你老母啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n判左未呀<br />\n<br />\n未審先判你當你自己法官"},{"pid":"6e9db21a1d9be4fd16a62c36a90106ed0ee79501","tid":316914,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:21:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>黑警死全家<br />\n暗角打擭 光明磊落？<br />\n屌你老母啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n判左未呀<br />\n<br />\n未審先判你當你自己法官</blockquote><br />\nYes <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b70d83849942696b2d37a655cd7d101c5341acb","tid":316914,"uid":364